Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.75,0:01:59.76,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}The Door to a New World
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.82,0:02:25.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,How dare they do that right in front of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.07,0:02:28.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is {\i1}exactly{\i0} why I was against Chor Rubor and Chor Caput being disbanded!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.32,0:02:34.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,We can't have Chor Tempest be the only ones we can depend on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.99,0:02:36.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Gather all the troops and the Simile!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.56,0:02:39.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,The reconnaissance Simile and the cruising Simile! All of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.13,0:02:40.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.93,0:02:42.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,What foolishness!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.85,0:02:47.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,I hope you realize that fighting leads absolutely nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.89,0:03:04.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Onashia...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.60,0:03:12.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wow, look at {\i1}that{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.42,0:03:13.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,Come one, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.46,0:03:15.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}am{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.80,0:03:21.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Over here, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.42,0:03:27.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,I said no playing on the Simoun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.68,0:03:28.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.78,0:03:30.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.34,0:03:31.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah c'mon, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.62,0:03:33.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well... because...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.64,0:03:36.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,Ummm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.19,0:03:40.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.36,0:03:41.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.61,0:03:42.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,"Booooou...!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.70,0:03:43.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's making a noise!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.74,0:03:45.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Like, "booooou!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.36,0:03:46.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.37,0:03:49.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wow, it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.44,0:03:50.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Like, "booooou!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.97,0:03:52.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,It sounds like a flute!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.84,0:03:54.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,C'mon! You too, Limone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.59,0:04:05.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, well?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.26,0:04:08.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,"Booooou..."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.41,0:04:09.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's what it sounds like.
Comment: 0,0:04:10.90,0:04:11.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Told ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.37,0:04:14.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Maybe there's something inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.63,0:04:45.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.40,0:04:48.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,So the day has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.33,0:04:52.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Would you please give us a little more time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.32,0:04:57.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,Would it be okay for us to come after we've finished our meal?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.08,0:05:06.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Did the meeting end badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.38,0:05:10.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Onashia is the symbol of the Simulacrum Theocracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.07,0:05:14.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm sure the authorities have been enjoying her continuing silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.16,0:05:18.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,But if she decides to act...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.63,0:05:22.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,I take no pleasure in warfare. However...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.22,0:05:26.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,To bring her here for a reason like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.02,0:05:29.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't fathom what Her Eminence is thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.06,0:05:31.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Guragief.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.59,0:05:32.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,If I should...
Comment: 0,0:05:32.84,0:05:33.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.43,0:05:36.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.47,0:06:01.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Never in {\i1}history{\i0} has anyone flown out in a Simoun without orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.63,0:06:03.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Have you no sense of responsibility?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.54,0:06:05.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Responsibility?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:08.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Our responsibility as Simoun sibyllae.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.94,0:06:12.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Pride in what we are. That which each of us bears.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.60,0:06:19.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Was that all that you wanted to say to us, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.61,0:06:21.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,In that case, please excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.84,0:06:31.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why, those little...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.96,0:06:42.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Paraietta?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.70,0:06:46.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Vyura!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.92,0:06:49.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,And... Rodoreamon and Alti as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.51,0:06:51.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,You too, Paraietta?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.76,0:06:54.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Couldn't sleep, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.55,0:06:56.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Us, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.39,0:07:00.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.80,0:07:07.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, it looks like everyone's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.52,0:07:41.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,The {\i1}Messis{\i0} will bear Onashia to her destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.82,0:07:44.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Neviril, Sibylla Aaeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.36,0:07:48.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Would you care to accompany her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.19,0:07:54.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,And would you like to know about... another world?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.01,0:07:58.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Could I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.62,0:08:00.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,...come along, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.62,0:08:01.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.66,0:08:02.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.62,0:08:04.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Those we have will suffice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.71,0:08:07.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.30,0:08:27.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.25,0:08:29.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.76,0:08:31.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Good...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.94,0:08:33.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,...isn't the word I'd use.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.86,0:08:36.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's bitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.14,0:08:37.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,Kind of, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.32,0:08:41.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,And it's sweet too... I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.98,0:08:45.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Bit it's not a taste I really hate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.16,0:08:46.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'll probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.28,0:08:48.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,...be able to finish eating it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.92,0:08:51.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,"Dunno."
Comment: 0,0:08:52.59,0:08:53.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.47,0:08:56.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,You never say that any more, Limone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.56,0:09:03.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,I started thinking about things more, and I feel like... there isn't much I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.16,0:09:04.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.78,0:09:06.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.88,0:09:11.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,The more I think, the more confused I become.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.49,0:09:15.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dominura?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.78,0:09:22.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, we'd best get going as soon as we've finished eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.47,0:09:23.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where to?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.80,0:09:29.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.53,0:09:37.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Her Eminence has ordered us to avoid "flying recklessly."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.54,0:09:41.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,I wonder where we're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.78,0:09:54.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.69,0:09:56.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.60,0:10:00.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,Onashia-sama is currently resting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.64,0:10:01.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.25,0:10:20.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Onashia.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.78,0:10:25.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,I wonder how "another world" is connected to all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.15,0:10:27.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,I feel really uneasy around the High Priestess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.02,0:10:32.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Defence Minister is kind of a bastard, but Her Eminence...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.79,0:10:34.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hmm, how should I put it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.40,0:10:39.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.80,0:10:42.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Your hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.11,0:10:43.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're so small.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.16,0:10:48.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,Stop treating me like a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.81,0:10:54.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,This war... it makes such obvious things hard to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.14,0:11:03.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Onashia...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.45,0:11:08.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,You have something you wish to ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.38,0:11:12.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,You told me that you can hear Mamiina's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.77,0:11:13.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,If so, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.85,0:11:15.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,...what about my comrades?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.53,0:11:20.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Have their souls... been set free?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.31,0:11:29.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You{\i0} are the one who wants to be set free, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.32,0:11:36.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,You keep trying to live close to the time and place where your friends died.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.69,0:11:40.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yet at the same time, you long to escape to a place far away from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.55,0:11:54.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Onashia-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.91,0:11:56.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,It seems that we have arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.81,0:12:44.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why have we come to the Ruins?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.28,0:12:54.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's doing it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.10,0:12:56.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,"The Door to a New World."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.54,0:13:00.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's the melody played by that music box.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.17,0:13:06.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,And the unsuspected goal of those who perished here.
Comment: 0,0:13:06.25,0:13:06.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.80,0:13:08.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.41,0:13:11.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,This place was once the training ground for Chor Dextra.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.59,0:13:13.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Chor... Dextra?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.81,0:13:18.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aaeru, your grandfather was the regina of that choir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.77,0:13:21.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Grandpa... was the regina?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.28,0:13:38.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.04,0:13:39.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.18,0:13:42.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,What happened back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.96,0:13:44.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,When do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.41,0:13:46.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,On the {\i1}Messis{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.62,0:13:50.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Everything just poured into me...
Comment: 0,0:13:50.47,0:13:51.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.76,0:13:55.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,When I looked inside the helical motor,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.01,0:13:57.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,it was as though I saw someone's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.96,0:13:59.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,...or some{\i1}thing's{\i0} memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.97,0:14:05.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,The only thing that's in there is a helix.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.15,0:14:08.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,All we can understand about it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.49,0:14:12.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Dominura?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.66,0:14:30.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dominura?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.16,0:14:40.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,We became obsessed by the Ri Maajon... by the Simoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.72,0:14:44.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,But that was because the Simoun were all that we had to rely on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.15,0:14:49.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes. If the Simoun had never existed in the first place...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.55,0:14:55.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Or if they had existed, but no one had been around to explain how they worked, what would have happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.44,0:14:58.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh? Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.17,0:15:00.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Ummm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.88,0:15:02.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.63,0:15:05.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,They'd...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.43,0:15:20.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,We brought them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.52,0:15:21.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.24,0:15:39.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A long, long time ago...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.93,0:15:42.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...there was a civilization vastly more advanced than ours.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.87,0:15:46.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It is said that the Simoun are relics from those days.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.98,0:15:53.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,But an unending series of wars broke out, and left the world in ruins.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.04,0:15:56.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,With everything destroyed, the land became worthless,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.06,0:15:59.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,and further war became pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.15,0:16:01.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Simoun were of no use to the starving masses,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.92,0:16:03.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,and the reason for their existence was forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.07,0:16:09.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,The people could do nothing more than wait for death to claim them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.07,0:16:20.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,And then, from the sky, it is said that a Simoun appeared from another world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.29,0:16:26.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Within it rode a pair of maidens, descending from heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.16,0:16:27.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Those girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.08,0:16:33.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They introduced themselves as "Simoun sibyllae."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.26,0:16:34.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And then...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.88,0:16:37.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,they imparted the secret of the Emerald Ri Maajon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.05,0:16:39.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Emerald Ri Maajon?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.10,0:16:40.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.40,0:16:41.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Another world...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.73,0:16:42.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.70,0:16:46.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,The ultimate Ri Maajon transports you to another {\i1}time{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.07,0:16:51.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,It is a divine gift that we have been granted—a great "what if?".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.75,0:16:58.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If the people of that time had been told that there would be another war...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.83,0:17:02.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,If the Simoun didn't exist...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.62,0:17:05.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Perhaps I wouldn't exist, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.33,0:17:10.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If, at that time, someone had been able to prevent people from relying on the Simoun...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.05,0:17:18.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,But if I didn't exist,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.13,0:17:20.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,then this pain I feel wouldn't have to exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.48,0:17:25.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...then our present, with all its extreme distress and poverty, might be very different.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.79,0:17:27.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,By travelling through time and space...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.50,0:17:31.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,...we can take this power of "what if?" to another age.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.07,0:17:33.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,That is the purpose of the Simoun,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.13,0:17:36.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,and of the Emerald Ri Maajon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.57,0:17:38.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,"Travelling across time and space...?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.46,0:17:39.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.92,0:17:40.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.87,0:17:41.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.63,0:17:44.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then this "Chor Dextra" that Grandpa commanded...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.93,0:17:50.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Chor Dextra was a choir created specifically to complete the Emerald Ri Maajon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.91,0:17:54.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Someone you all know very well once belonged to that choir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.84,0:17:55.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.34,0:17:58.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Dominura.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.27,0:18:01.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,She is the only surviving member of Chor Dextra.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.57,0:18:07.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dominura?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:12.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes. I finally realised...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.41,0:18:26.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,...that everything happened because {\i1}I{\i0} started it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.20,0:18:45.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.13,0:18:49.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking about what you said before, Dominura.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.39,0:18:52.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,About "what if the Simoun didn't exist?"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.20,0:18:55.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,If they had never existed?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.07,0:18:57.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Uh huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.11,0:19:00.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then... I would never have met everyone in Chor Tempest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.74,0:19:05.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,And... I wouldn't have met you either, Dominura.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.50,0:19:13.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.99,0:19:16.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, why am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.73,0:19:19.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,U-ummm...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.00,0:19:20.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because you're sad?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.59,0:19:22.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because you're lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.30,0:19:23.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because it hurts?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.89,0:19:25.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Or, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.25,0:19:26.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Ummm...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:30.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because you're... happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.57,0:19:32.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.25,0:19:34.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.76,0:19:39.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.62,0:19:43.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,You still don't know where we're gonna go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.28,0:19:44.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.74,0:19:45.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,Now I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.34,0:20:49.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Dominura has probably completed the Emerald Ri Maajon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.33,0:20:50.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.99,0:20:53.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,...that she is alive, in some other time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.02,0:20:54.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.35,0:20:59.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Dominura and Sibylla Limone are alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.67,0:21:01.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,I do not believe that I am mistaken about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.88,0:21:03.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.49,0:21:06.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Amuria might be too?
Comment: 0,0:21:05.53,0:21:06.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.32,0:21:08.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Does that mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.16,0:21:11.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,...that it's possible that Amuria is still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.74,0:21:19.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Emerald Ri Maajon is the one hope given to us by Tempus Spatium.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.71,0:21:25.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Whether it takes you into the future or into the past is beyond anyone's control.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.28,0:21:31.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,However, the Simoun exist through the will of Tempus Spatium.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.11,0:21:35.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,And it is not likely that the gods would err.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.02,0:21:41.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,Tempus Spatium will undoubtedly open the door to the right time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.69,0:21:45.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Neviril, Sibylla Aaeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.85,0:21:48.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to entrust this to you:
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.40,0:21:52.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Emerald Ri Maajon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.96,0:22:03.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.13,0:22:07.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,A Simoun from the {\i1}Arcus Niger{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.63,0:22:09.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Minister!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.65,0:22:11.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,What... what is this? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.80,0:22:14.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,The {\i1}Arcus Niger{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.40,0:22:16.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,...has gone down.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.77,0:22:22.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Seven o'clock high! Five ancient Simoun, closing in fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.44,0:22:23.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
